scenarios need to cover

| Threat         | Solution                         |
| -------------- | -------------------------------- |
| Multithreading | Double-Checked Locking or Holder |
| Serialization  | `readResolve()` or Enum          |
| Cloning        | Override `clone()` or use Enum   |
| Reflection     | Constructor guard or use Enum    |
| Inheritance    | Make class `final` or use Enum   |
